SSH Between Two Virtual Machines 
(secure shell and secure copy )

virtual machine 1     
steps
1 
ip --brief addr show
( ssh 2nd system name@ 2nd system ip )
eg.   ssh om@192.168.35.244
exit
----------
cd /tmp 
ls -l om

==========================
==========================
virtual machine 2 
steps
1
ip --brief addr show
-----------------------
scp -r  /home/om2 192.168.32.169:/tem
(scp -r ( copy the folder ) /home/system1_name  system1_ip:/dir_name)
